This year four awards were presented at the 2000 annual meeting of the National Association of Abandoned Mine Land Programs.
National and Appalachian Region Awards
s The Kentucky Department for Surface Mining Reclamation and Enforcement's Pleasant View Mine Project near the city of Madisonville, Ken-
